    • Method Detail

      • unknownTask

        public static MesosEventClient.TaskStatusResponse unknownTask()
        Tells the caller that this client did not recognize task described by this status. The caller should kill the task so that its reserved resources will be offered by Mesos, at which point those resources will be unreserved via the unexpected resources cleanup process.
